The,Meteorological,Assimilation,Data,Ingest,System,MADIS,is,a,service,of,NOAA,to,collect,integrate,provide,quality,control,for,and,distribute,meteorological,data,observations,MADIS,includes,data,provided,by,NOAA,as,well,as,other,international,federal,state,and,local,agencies,universities,volunteers,and,the,private,sector,The,MADIS,API,is,used,via,Fortran,but,utility,programs,are,also,available,to,perform,single,instance,calls,and,output,responses,to,a,text,file